Portable mini fluid pump

Sometimes I need to add water to the aquarium. 
I didn't want to pull the hose out of the tap or fill a 10l pot with water. 
In the e-shop I discovered a small 12V DC water pump with a discharge of approx. 2.5L / Min. 
I thought of putting it in a box with a Li Ion battery, charger and DC / DC converter. 
And this is what ...

